translate ru Demonarc4_46633255:
    # "Sarah sat down on the heaped up pile of hay."
    ""

translate ru Demonarc4_b6e6f02e:
    # "Outside, the cold winds howled."
    ""

translate ru Demonarc4_0f17acfe:
    # "Sarah could feel the cold wind cut through the gaps and holes of the old ruined castle."
    ""

translate ru Demonarc4_78a2f0b6:
    # "Outside was probably worse, but inside was hardly better."
    ""

translate ru Demonarc4_66d1e2e0:
    # "From the corner of her eyes, she watched as Dalia climbed into her bed."
    ""

translate ru Demonarc4_c94330a9:
    # "A real bed. An actual bed."
    ""

translate ru Demonarc4_78ac0ce0:
    # "And instead, she was forced to sit and sleep on a pil of hay, as if she were some farm animal."
    ""

translate ru Demonarc4_9e40b937:
    # "A spike of resentment build in her."
    ""

translate ru Demonarc4_6bbd94e1:
    # "What made that girl think she was any better than her?"
    ""

translate ru Demonarc4_4fdffaa9:
    # "But it faded away just as quickly."
    ""

translate ru Demonarc4_ed3406aa:
    # "None of it was Dalia's fault."
    ""

translate ru Demonarc4_d5b37b41:
    # "If anything, this was likely just another game, played on them by the Master."
    ""

translate ru Demonarc4_d810ab2b:
    # "Pitching them against one another over some trivial thing."
    ""

translate ru Demonarc4_a08817ef:
    # "Driving a wedge between them."
    ""

